코로 숨쉬고 두 눈에 담았던 전 세계의 수많은 눈부신 풍경들. 잊을 수 없는 기억들. 지구야, 내년에도 잘 부탁해.
There are so many fabulous far away places to see
Such as Mexico, Sweden, Hawaii, Japan and Capri
There are so many exciting and wonderful places
Mountains and jungles, deserts and oases
Pleasant as home is, it isn’t what Rome is
So why stay there?
When there are so many fabulous far away places to see
Why should Spain and Tahiti and Rio,
Just be only names to you and me?
I feel certain there’s people we’d be glad to know there
So tell me why don’t we get up and just go there
Go to those fabulous places where we long to be
Like Bangkok, Hongkong, Paris and Venice
Tokyo and Cairo and Lisbon and London
Wonderful fabulous places we’re longing to be
Fabulous spaces / Kevin Spacey
